## Tech stack (001-gmail-standby-unread)

- Vue 3 + Vite + TypeScript + PWA (vite-plugin-pwa)
- Pinia, Vue Router, idb (IndexedDB)
- Gmail API: INBOX `messagesUnread` only; OAuth PKCE
- Sync: 60s foreground polling when visible + visibilitychange immediate refresh
- Notifications: Notification API (no C# Web Push in MVP)
- Modules: `public/modules/` → URL `/modules/`; manifest schema 1.0.0
- Default module: `public/modules/cat-pack/` (module-bundled Lottie renderer)
- Avatar core: `src/core/avatar`, `src/core/modules`, `src/core/render`

